This is to shuffle wallpaper set)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>If you have followed correctly so far then you should see something similar to this.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"All Automations Screen\" src=\"https://bn1302files.storage.live.com/y4m2jdKgIIWl6RXx3CxEo7nX-zadC2TD_KjsVJtnbjIotSU4guOXJNjIY4f6ZA23ENXBRopGx0Fk6fs4xfjiu6B50ja1IZaLD4siOWmE2qsq6CQYDwtEZ72ywIwyzt4gYclYDIOrzXF75WidVREMxYAwHT0MGylWJaf4RZaeltijhiiW-XvilREqHUwZ4BVMbct?width=295&amp;height=1024&amp;cropmode=none\"></p>\n<p><em>(Note: Make sure Ask Before Running is turned off in all automations)</em></p>\n<h4>Done setting up.</h4>\n<h4>You should see updated wallpaper periodically (early morning/morning/noon/evening/night).</h4>\n<hr>\n<h3>Recommended (Optional)</h3>\n<h4>Follow this if you are tired seeing lots of notifications from Shortcuts app.</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to Settings &gt; Screen Time &gt; See All Activity</li>\n<li>Find <strong>Shortcuts</strong> under <strong>Notifications</strong> section. If it's not there then try to switch days and find it.\n<img alt=\"Screen Time Shortcuts App under Notifications\" src=\"https://bn1302files.storage.live.com/y4mDJOoI_HJvsMwuAJx2ne0vYUQk8i0Vah_v-Ule3iIKatf_bnf5SGqiGWF4hlAWQAXBjcCpsb7BLUpNRBGZBsviF6ekvJHWQ7pRQ2FBGuT8T9ZRL1D3XeiVUcOFycsJxrnft-lcboI-zaplXNj8sYwQKSIEIP1ONziw6y8cJ2pE8xzvxBItoll1iz9OvYRsCiX?width=305&amp;height=660&amp;cropmode=none\"></li>\n<li>Turn of All Notifications</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h6>Have any idea to consider in following updates?</h6>\n<h6>Want to add your custom theme?</h6>\n<h6>Or, if you have any trouble setting it up or have any feedback/comments please send message in <strong>Feedback</strong> section.</h6>\n<h6>Medium Post</h6>\n<p>https://techai.medium.com/dynamic-wallpaper-automation-with-ios-shortcuts-5bf8d742d275   </p>\n<hr>\n<h3>FAQs</h3>\n<h5>On first run, getting this prompt - “Which pattern should the text be matched against?”</h5>\n<p>Restart your device and try to run again.</p>\n<h5>Shortcuts is showing no